                            <comment id="13424532" author="auke" created="Sun, 29 Jul 2012 12:27:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached patch fixes the current behavior.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are still some issues:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;paths should be relative to the config directory (or config/resources)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The method SynapseConfigUtils.getSynapseEnvironment is broken and the SynapseEnvironment isn&apos;t available until the whole configuration is built&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The method WSDLEndpointFactory.createEndpoint uses the property RESOLVE_ROOT as base uri when defining an inline WSDL definition, this doesn&apos;t make any sense (imports with relative paths in an inline definition don&apos;t make sense)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
